e=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">属猪的属相婚配表</u><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-top: 0px\">12生肖几月出生最好：</strong><br style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-top: 0px\" />\r\n<u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(37,110,177); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">属鼠的几月出生最好</u><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(37,110,177); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">属牛的几月出生最好</u><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(37,110,177); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">属虎的几月出生最好</u><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(37,110,177); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">属兔的几月出生最好</u><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</u><br style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" />\r\n<u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(37,110,177); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">属龙的几月出生最好</u><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(37,110,177); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">属蛇的几月出生最好</u><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(37,110,177); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">属马的几月出生最好</u><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(37,110,177); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">属羊的几月出生最好</u><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</u><br style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" />\r\n<u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(37,110,177); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">属猴的几月出生最好</u><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(37,110,177); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">属鸡的几月出生最好</u><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(37,110,177); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">属狗的几月出生最好</u><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(37,110,177); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\">属猪的几月出生最好</u></u>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"adb adb_3\"></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"pagelist\"></div>','10','0','0','0','2015-08-31 17:44:31','0');");
E_D("replace into `shengxiao_data` values('343','属鸡的几月出生最好？','<div class=\"sbody\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"adb adb_1\"></div>\r\n<div class=''adb adb_2''></div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 【导语】<u>属鸡</u>的几月出生最好。出生月份是影响着我们一生的<u>运势</u>，虽然说并不一定起着决定性作用，但是如果能促进我们的<u>好运</u>势，那当然是&ldquo;人见人爱，花见花开&rdquo;啦。假如刚好赶上自己<u>生肖</u>的最佳出生月份，那就眉笑颜开。没赶上的朋友也不要气馁，因为也有句话说&ldquo;人定胜天&rdquo;，最终命运还是掌握在自己手里的。<strong><u>属鸡的几月出生最好</u></strong>，114啦星座小编与大家一起揭晓。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n	<span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong>属鸡的几月出生最好（PS：月份为农历）<br />\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.xingzuowu.com/uploads/allimg/140509/2009-140509164K43A.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 370px\" /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 属鸡的几月出生最好：二月出生的鸡儿。</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 出生在二月的<u>肖鸡</u>朋友，一生都抱着自命不凡的心态，但是天资过人，有学识。因此，在这个月出生的肖鸡朋友，聪明好学，在学校是&ldquo;学霸&rdquo;，出来社会工作更是公司中的佼佼者。虽说没有祖业帮助，父母也不是很富裕，但是靠自己的能力，抓紧机遇，到了中晚年方可过上好日子。</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 属鸡的几月出生最好：四月出生的鸡儿。</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 四月出生的鸡儿，一生坎坷，但是有着超强的领导能力，有抱负，<u>性格</u>骄傲，经常给人目中无人的感觉。家中虽有小许家业，但是你的一生需要靠自己的技能发展，方可展现才华出众的一面。</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 属鸡的几月出生最好：九月出生的鸡儿。</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在<u>本月</u>出生的鸡儿，有着自己独特的思想，个性随和，尽管自己有才能，也不会狗眼看人低，给予别人亲切的感觉，不摆一点架子，能够一生无拘无束的过日子，一生幸运呢！<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 属鸡人正月出生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 出生于正月的属鸡人，一生并不会有着穷困，身体倍儿棒，延年益寿。正月属鸡人并无祖传<u>事业</u>，出外无贵人，只能靠自己成就。晚年享受天伦之乐，家庭和睦互相帮助，并无伟大事业，但生活丰富。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 属鸡人二月出生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 出生于二月的属鸡人，自命清高，但是本身有着聪明的脑袋，有着满肚子的水墨，好学。可惜并无好机会，也无祖传事业可继承，没有父母相助，难当伟大之人。在中年时期才学有所用，<u>性格</u>孤僻，不愿和平庸之人相处。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 属鸡人三月出生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 出生于三月的属鸡人，有着随机应变的能力，懂得怎么跟上社会的节奏。三月属鸡人是一个很幸运的人，好学有文化，有着官运。有家庭相助，有朋友贵人相助，事业路平顺，不愁吃喝。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 属鸡人四月出生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 出生于四月的属鸡人，一生并不平坦，难成大事，虽有组织能力，有着志气与理想，但性格骄傲，自我为中心，有着才华却无处发挥。虽有继承祖业，但并不庞大，靠自己一门手艺才能，<u>财运</u>不多，四月属鸡人爱冒险。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 属鸡人五月出生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 出生于五月的属鸡人，一生人命运大起大落，有时富贵有时贫。可得到家庭相助，有着美满的大家族，上半生事业运成功一时，便会失败，下半生有贵人相助，事业路平顺却没太大进展，一生有吃有穿，运气不大好。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 属鸡人六月出生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 出生于六月的属鸡人，一辈子忙碌奔波，并无安稳日子。没有家庭相助，没有贵人相助，在事业上的路比较坎坷。一生人中有着难于意料的挫折，让属鸡人的心灵受创难以平复，只要有毅力就能成就事业。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 属鸡人七月出生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 出生于七月的属鸡人，一生人平稳，不愁吃喝，幸福一生。祖传事业遗产丰富，家庭和睦，倾力相助属鸡人，不用奔波就能够享受荣华富贵。事业心强，有家庭相助，事业平顺发展，有成绩。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 属鸡人八月出生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 出生于八月的属鸡人，一生荣华富贵，受人钦佩。并无祖传事业，难有家庭相助。但八月属鸡人勤奋，有过人志气，不怕困难，在事业路上有贵人相助，排遣万难，顺利发展。一生人无病无灾，名利双收。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 属鸡人九月出生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 出生于九月的属鸡人，乃大富翁，一生人并无坎坷而言。虽无祖传事业继承，但有贵人相助扶持，快乐一生。性格刚直，脾气暴躁，很自我，或者就因如此，财运极佳，没有困境，幸福一辈子。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 属鸡人十月出生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 出生于十月的属鸡人，则平淡无奇度过一生，并无太大的志气与理想，不好学，一切顺其自然，没祖业继承，但又兄弟姐妹相助。在中年之后能有幸福生活，财运平平，足够吃喝，身体健康，无大病。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 属鸡人十一月出生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 出生于十一月的属鸡人，有志气有理想，虽有祖业继承，但根基差，无法靠家庭，在外也没贵人，全是靠自己，拼搏途中经常有孤独感。会经常跟人发生金钱纠纷，有着破财迹象。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 属鸡人十二月出生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/31px 宋体, Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(81,81,81); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 出生于十二月的属鸡人，一生为了名利奔波劳碌，虽然不愁吃喝，但不会享受。父母无力相助，兄弟姐妹也少帮助，一生人在事业上并不平顺，性格很忠厚耿直。中年会有一灾，晚年能有经济却不会享受。<br />\r\n	<strong><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\"><strong><u><font size=\"3\">属鸡的人2014年运程</font></u></strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">1957年属鸡的人2014年运程</u></span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">1969年属<u><font color=\"#256eb1\">鸡</font></u>的人2014年运程</u></span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">1981年属<u><font color=\"#256eb1\">鸡</font></u>的人2014年运程</u></u></span><br />\r\n	<span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">1993年属<u><font color=\"#256eb1\">鸡</font></u>的人2014年运程</u></span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">2005年属<u><font color=\"#256eb1\">鸡</font></u>的人2014年运程</u><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-decoration: none; padding-top: 0px\"><strong><u><font size=\"3\">属鸡的人2015年运程</font></u></strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">1957年属鸡的人2015年运程</u></span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">1969年属<u><font color=\"#256eb1\">鸡</font></u>的人2015年运程</u></span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">1981年属<u><font color=\"#256eb1\">鸡</font></u>的人2015年运程</u></span><br />\r\n	<span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">1993年属<u><font color=\"#256eb1\">鸡</font></u>的人2015年运程</u></span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<u style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">20